{
  "stem": "43.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I was three days, I didn't have any water, any peace of bread.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I-- I asked Yonah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was-- he was then eight years old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he was smarter than I am.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I asked him, what shall we do?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Shall I go?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or you want to go-- what you-- what shall we do?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, Mamala.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mamala we called, Mamalatata.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You go, and I will take care of Sossela.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was the third day I went out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I, a whole day, went with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I see how to come in the night, go out in the night to come back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The forest is so big.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What-- what I-- so I try.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I-- I got-- a Ukraine gave me such a shawl-- what they working alone out-- how heavy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So when I came out, he told me he will sit it at the-- near the-- the tree.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was alone then with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he was holding Sossela.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I put here a little hat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- and he's-- he want to hold this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I took her.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And-- and I got a few shmatas-- what Nadia gave me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I covered them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was snowing a little.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It started snowing in the night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I took my shawl and put the place when I go out from the forest.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But when the snow is snow, everything was covered.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "When I came around 3:00-- 3:00 in the night or 3:00/3:30 something, and then I didn't know where to come in and where to go out, and where-- where-- where I left my children.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I couldn't find the-- the same way, because it was snow there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I am without stockings and without shoes now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There was a shmata from the snow.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
